Terraform:
 - IaC - change,build cloud and on premises
 - It is wokring through API
 - workflow of Terraform 
      write -> plan -> Apply
 - It is immutable approach - create new infra
 - Infra is getting tracked by STATE FILE
 - Config file describe th infra end
 - Modules - Reuse of config
Configuration Language:
  - To declare resources in infrastructure

resource "aws_vpc" "main" {
  cidr_block = var.base_cidr_block
}

<BLOCK TYPE> "<BLOCK LABEL>" "<BLOCK LABEL>" {
  # Block body
  <IDENTIFIER> = <EXPRESSION> # Argument
}

Blocks - Container of content like resource
  * Block type * Block label *Identifier *Expression * Argument
